    <briefdescription>
<para>Provides functions for convolution operations on arrays. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="author"><para>Otto Link (<ulink url="mailto:otto.link.bv@gmail.com">otto.link.bv@gmail.com</ulink>) </para>
</simplesect>
This header file defines functions for performing convolution operations on 1D and 2D arrays using various kernels. The operations include 1D convolutions along different directions, 2D convolutions with symmetry boundary conditions, truncated 2D convolutions, and approximate convolutions using Singular Value Decomposition (SVD).</para>
